OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and breezy day for
OL,6,Fmany. Plenty of sunny spells
OL,7,Fthroughout, but perhaps the odd
OL,8,Fpassing shower towards Anglesey.
OL,9,FFeeling a little chilly despite the
OL,10,Fspells sunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and chilly evening to
OL,13,Fcome. However, overnight cloud will
OL,14,Fthicken from the west with some patchy
OL,15,Frain and drizzle developing during the
OL,16,Fearly hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
