OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dull and damp start to the
OL,6,Fday. However, it should become drier
OL,7,Fand brighter through the morning with
OL,8,Fa few sunny spells developing for the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRather
OL,12,Fcloudy on Wednesday, with rain likely
OL,13,Fby the evening. A frosty start on
OL,14,FThursday but then fine and sunny.
OL,15,FOvernight rain clearing to sunny
OL,16,Fspells on Friday. Turning colder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
